works.description:
We have seen a range of automobile themed  
furniture in the past, and the latest we have is the Bugatti inspired  
Executive Desk from Luzzo Bespoke. The bespoke desk takes styling cues from  
the Bugatti Grand Prix racing cars of the late ‘20s and early ‘30s. Details  
taken from the design of the cars were used in different forms or scales  
within the design. The drive gears for the height adjustment are a  
scaled-up version of the Winfield carburetor synchronization quadrants from  
a Type 57, and the drawer fronts reflect the honeycombed grill.
